a105 2
   * NSF recently increased its [[http://www.nsf.gov/pubs/policydocs/pappguide/nsf11001/gpg_2.jsp#IIC2j requirements for data-sharing plans]] in grant proposals (see Appendix 1); (to include trees? jsw)
   * In recent years, NESCent has invested in "phyloinformatics" efforts to enable interoperability, resulting in projects to develop an XML file format (NeXML), an ontology (CDAO) and a web-services standard (PhyloWS).  
